info.description:
Pygments Delegate Formatter
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Pygments Delegate Formatter plugs into the Pygments syntax highlighting
package written in Python.

It provides a formatter to ….

Install the `Pygments Delegate Formatter tip`_ via ``easy_install Pygments-Delegate-Formatter==dev``.

.. _Pygments Delegate Formatter tip:
   http://bitbucket.org/sjorek/pygments-delegate-formatter/get/tip.zip#egg=Pygments-Delegate-Formatter-dev
